{"tid":2262560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑因受不了侵權　全球最大五金工具企業關閉深圳廠數千人失業","createTime":"2020-10-29T08:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T09:02:03.000Z","uid":271829,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e89db7ad1e7b77f4037ee1d1cd6af740ce96db77","tid":2262560,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:06:46.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n中國廣東媒體上月為了慶祝深圳特區成立40周年，曾對全球最大五金工具企業「史丹利百得」（Stanley Black &amp; Decker）在當地的工廠進行專題報導，當時公司高層才表示，將擴大對自動化和數位化的投入。不過該公司本周一（26日）突然發公告宣佈解散深圳子公司，估計數千名員工恐一夜間失業。有分析認為，史丹利百得是因為忍受不了中國的侵權行為，加上美中關係不明朗，所以決定撤離中國。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201029/WHTD3OGUIFCDJNQVKJ7MVBSFDU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201029%2FWHTD3OGUIFCDJNQVKJ7MVBSFDU%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kii8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=f3339464\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201029%2FWHTD3OGUIFCDJNQVKJ7MVBSFDU%2F&h=7435ad0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201029/WHTD3OGUIFCDJNQVKJ7MVBSFDU/</a>"},{"pid":"112aad85159e7cee03430713ed856f69542d84bc","tid":2262560,"uid":180851,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話來就來 走就走<br />\n當我地大中華係乜地方<br />\n所有洋鬼通通滾"},{"pid":"739b289a6d76cdfd4cf7edf383b4beb2e71f4665","tid":2262560,"uid":66378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:18:07.000Z","msg":"搬....腳"},{"pid":"0848baf22950dad9091f18b91c7643aed6da99f8","tid":2262560,"uid":253608,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:19:53.000Z","msg":"當時公司高層才表示，將擴大對自動化和數位化的投入。不過該公司本周一（26日）突然發公告宣佈解散深圳子公司<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"h